### Get pages by slug (example)
GET {{wpSite}}/wp-json/wp/v2/pages?slug=home
Authorization: Basic {{authBasic}}

### Create a draft page (replace auth with app password)
POST {{wpSite}}/wp-json/wp/v2/pages
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Basic {{authBasic}}

{
  "title": "Home (Test)",
  "status": "draft",
  "content": "<p>Test publish from REST Client.</p>",
  "slug": "home-test"
}

### Update page example (replace {id} with page ID)
POST {{wpSite}}/wp-json/wp/v2/pages/{id}
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Basic {{authBasic}}

{
  "content": "<p>Updated content from REST Client.</p>"
}
